title: Aliyah Burke - Combustion {2bUnique}
description:
Combustion by Aliyah Burke, McKenna Jeffries, and Taige Crenshaw

Genre: Paranormal
Series: Savoy Valley - Book 6
Length: Novel
Price: Free
Publication Date: November 4, 2011 - December 30, 2011
Cover art by MMJ Designs

Two fire beings in close proximity, can they withstand the heat?

Saskia Van der Ness has returned home a changed woman. Her new status as a phoenix had come at an incredible price, the loss of her parents. Angry and feeling more alone than ever, can she learn to accept the help offered her before she self destructs?

Damu Kijani was a red dragon. An ancient. Not a dragon shifter, no, he was a dragon who on occasion takes human form. From the moment he met, Saskia, he knew she was his mate, his queen. His. There was one problem, she didn't agree.

Circumstances put them together even though she fights it and Damu decides the only way to help Saskia see and reach her true potential is to help her himself. Their close quarters inflames the passion between them but he refuses to pursue her, wanting her to discover her need for him. When it all comes together will they be able to survive the combustion?
